Direct Known Subclasses:
PlAtom, PlJavaObj, PlNumber
public abstract class PlAtomic
extends PlStruct

Representa objetos atomicos de prolog. Existen tres clases de objetos atomicos: Atomos (PlAtom), Números (PlNumber) y Objetos Java (PlJavaObj)
